name: Bolognese Sauce
description: A pasta dish combined with meat sauce. Eating it makes it difficult for sanity to decrease and provides COMMON_STATUS_RANGE_ATTACK +10% for a while.

name: Caprity Meat
description:
BerryGoat meat.
Healthy and full of nutrients.
Hints of berries scenting the meat stimulates the appetite.

name: Rushoar Pork
description:
Boar meat.
Full of the delicious flavors of wild game.
Juicy and nutritious.

name: Chikipi Poultry
description:
ChickenPal meat.
Light and easy to eat,
it's a local favorite for residents of Palpagos Island.

name: Mozzarina Meat
description:
CowPal meat.
Thick, juicy and marbled.
Residents of Palpagos Island cherish it above all other meats.

name: Eikthyrdeer Venison
description:
Deer meat.
Light and lean, but rich in flavor.

name: Galeclaw Poultry
description:
Eagle meat.
Full of nutrition, its flavor packs a punch.

name: Mammorest Meat
description:
GrassMammoth meat.
With massive size comes massive flavor.
Its overwhelming portions are sure to satisfy any glutton.

name: Reindrix Venison
description:
IceDeer meat.
Strange venison capable of remaining at low temperatures.
Takes a very long time to spoil.

name: Raw Kelpsea
description:
Kelpie meat.
Tender and slightly sweet.
Fish meat tends to spoil quickly.

name: Raw Dumud
description:
LazyCatfish meat.
Fatty with a rich taste.
Has a mouthwatering plump texture.

name: Broncherry Meat
description:
SakuraSaurus meat.
Giant meat full of massive stores of energy.
Stuffed to the brim with nutrients gathered through photosynthesis.

name: Lamball Mutton
description:
SheepBall meat.
Red meat with a unique flavor.
Delicious, but takes some getting used to.

name: Medical Supplies
description:
Strange Medicines that are effective at treating COMMON_CONDITION_NAME_GastricUlcer and COMMON_CONDITION_NAME_Fracture.
they do not heal Health.

name: Milk
description:
Drink it as is, or use it in various meals.
Can be milked from CowPal.

name: Mind Control Meds
description:
MindControlDrug that are extremely effective in controlling dissidents.
they do not heal Health.

name: Gold Coin
description:
Currency traded on Palpagos Island.
Can be exchanged for items or Pals with merchants.

name: Mushroom
description:
A mushroom that can be eaten raw.
They can be found anywhere on the island.

name: Mushroom Soup
description: Cream soup made of Mushroom. When eaten, it raises the work speed and improves the stomach fullness for a certain time.

name: Mushroom Stew
description: A stew made with Mushroom. Consumption elevates work speed and offers COMMON_STATUS_RANGE_ATTACK +10% for a particular duration.

name: Musket
description: An old-fashioned, simple gun. Powerful in a single shot, but the reload time is lengthy.

name: Strange Juice
description:
Juice that greatly improves mood when consumed.
Drinking it significantly increases work speed for a period of time,
but significantly lowers SAN.

name: Night Vision Goggles
description: Night Vision Goggles

name: Omelet
description: A dish where Egg is fried and ketchup is added. Eating it results in a temporary COMMON_STATUS_RANGE_ATTACK -5%, COMMON_STATUS_DEFENCE+15%.

name: Suspicious Juice
description:
Juice that improves mood when consumed.
Drinking it greatly increases work speed for a period of time,
but lowers SAN.

name: Ancient Civilization Parts
description:
Debris excavated from ancient ruins.
Contains abundant information on lost technology.
Extremely valuable, people from all walks of life are now seeking such crystals.

name: Pal Fluids
description:
Body fluids taken from a Pal.
Useful for its high viscosity.

name: Penking Plume
description:
Plume dropped from a CaptainPenguin.
Used to make clothing.

name: Katress Hair
description:
Hair dropped from a CatMage.
Used to make clothing.

name: Tocotoco Feather
description:
Feathers dropped from a ColorfulBird.
Used to make clothing, as the beautifully vivid colors are quite popular.

name: Gumoss Leaf
description:
Leaves dropped from a PlantSlime.
Used to make clothing.

name: Precious Dragon Stone
description:
A gemstone-like ball collected from Pals.
Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

name: Precious Plume
description:
Glittering feathers collected from Pals.
Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

name: Precious Entrails
description:
A heart that never stops beating collected from Pals.
Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

name: Precious Claw
description:
Extremely sharp claws collected from Pals.
Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

name: Precious Pelt
description:
Fluffy fur collected from Pals.
Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

name: High Quality Pal Oil
description:
High-quality oil that can be extracted from Pal.
Necessary for making Polymer.

name: Pal Sphere
description:
An item that captures Pals when thrown.
Mass produced, it is only effective on low level Pals.

name: Pal Sphere
description: en Text

name: Giga Sphere
description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown.
Able to capture moderately powerful Pals.

name: Legendary Sphere
description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown.
It has extremely powerful capturing capabilities,
leaving almost no Pal able to escape.

name: Ultra Sphere
description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown.
With powerful abilities, not many Pals are able to escape it.

name: Mega Sphere
description:
An item that captures Pals when thrown.
Its capabilities have been improved, allowing it to catch a wider range of Pals.

name: Radar Sphere
description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown.
Though it has a low chance of success,
it can forcibly capture another person’s Pal.

name: Hyper Sphere
description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown.
Able to capture very powerful Pals.

name: Small Pal Soul
description:
A spirit left behind by a small Pal.
It can draw out hidden abilities if offered to a BuildableGoddessStatue.

name: Medium Pal Soul
description:
